    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I see. It sounds like you're suggesting there might be some inherent friction between their backgrounds and our specific corporate environment. If we were to present these three candidates to our executive board, which one do you think would be considered the \"safest\" bet for a high-level leadership position, and which one poses the most risk to our current culture?",
